---
metadata: {
    partial_name: 'Ecommerce | Products | Enrich Cards'
}
---
{% comment %}
    Runs the per-page batch queries that power the enhanced product card
    (tags + low_stock_override, approved review ratings, completed-order sold
    counts) for a set of products, keyed by product uuid, so the card can look
    up its own values without an N+1 across the grid/carousel. Shared by
    products/grid.liquid and the New arrivals / What's hot / You may also like /
    Purchase again blocks.

    Pass EITHER:
    - products      : array of product results (uuid is mapped out), OR
    - product_uuids : array of product uuids (e.g. from ordered items)

    Exports (read via context.exports.*):
    - cf_rows      : product_custom_field rows (tags, low_stock_override)
    - review_rows  : approved review ratings (reviewed_product, rating)
    - sold_rows    : completed-order line items (product_uuid, quantity)
{% endcomment %}
{%- comment -%}
    Derive uuids from `products` when given (overriding any `product_uuids` that
    leaked in from a parent scope, e.g. the PDP setting its own product_uuids
    before including 'You may also like'). Callers that have no products array
    (e.g. Purchase again) pass `product_uuids` directly instead.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if products -%}
    {%- assign product_uuids = products | map: 'uuid' -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- assign cf_rows = '' | split: ',' -%}
{%- assign review_rows = '' | split: ',' -%}
{%- assign sold_rows = '' | split: ',' -%}
{%- if product_uuids and product_uuids.size > 0 -%}
    {%- graphql cf_rows = 'modules/ecommerce/products/get_products_custom_fields', product_uuids: product_uuids | dig: 'items', 'results' -%}
    {%- graphql review_rows = 'modules/ecommerce/reviews/get_products_review_summary', product_uuids: product_uuids | dig: 'items', 'results' -%}
    {%- graphql sold_rows = 'modules/ecommerce/order_items/get_products_sold_count', product_uuids: product_uuids | dig: 'items', 'results' -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- export cf_rows -%}
{%- export review_rows -%}
{%- export sold_rows -%}
